reviewText: Outstanding Biography and plays with no errors. Thanks for your business.
What to say but brand new. The case is great and tape plaied so very well. Thank you so very much. ART

Be aware: this is not a DVD but simply a DVD-R. No remastering (image quality is the same as the old videocassette), no subtitles at all (I'm a little deaf).
To be avoided, in my opinion.
